{"tid":1574203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵係香港交通嘅核心 好難罷撘","createTime":"2019-09-16T10:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T10:19:58.000Z","uid":289900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4024539931283521c666ee55706bdceadf654cdf","tid":1574203,"uid":289900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好屌著 睇埋先</span></strong></span><br />\n.<br />\n黨鐵作為香港公共交通工具核心中嘅核心<br />\n市區定新市鎮都係以MTR沿線發展<br />\n巴士只留於區域內服務(例：地鐵站返自己屋邨)<br />\n同長途巴士提供唔洗轉車直達服務(例：北區去港島返工，坐978直達中環，唔洗火車再轉觀塘再轉荃灣綫)<br />\n而且巴士公司以黨鐵服務為由不斷cut班次(例：南港島綫開通，南區人轉坐黨鐵，導致巴士公司決定減車)<br />\n而小巴嘅定位根本寫明係「主要作為巴士和鐵路的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輔助</span></span></span>和<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">接駁</span></span>工具」<br />\n如果唔坐黨鐵，小巴同巴士加埋都唔可能取代黨鐵作為香港公共交通核心嘅地位<br />\n所以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日跳左閘未</span></strong></span><br />\n唔敢跳就全民今個月<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">65歲</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d2a98d7e8f2ddc184edd0d466f6bf0252b07f4","tid":1574203,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T10:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月